SEND.LABELPLACEHOLDER: Faka ileyibhile yale dilesi ukuyifaka kwincwadi yakho yee dilesi
SEND.INPUTLOCKED: Input ivaliwe. Uya kufuna ukuvula le ngcaciso ukuze uyisebenzise.
SEND.ALERTFEECHANGECONTENT: Imali yokuthengiselana eyona nto iphakamileyo kunokuba ilindeleke. Nceda uqinisekise umrhumo omtsha:

STAKING.NOTENABLEDINFO: Ukwenziwa komgca okwangoku akunikwe amandla okwangoku.
STAKING.NOTENABLEDINSTR: Ukugxininisa uza kuyidinga ukukhupha isitatimende se staking = 1 kwifayile yakho yemetrix.conf.
STAKING.NOTSTAKINGINSTR: Unokuqala ukuphawula ngokuvula i-wallet yakho yokumisa

MASTERNODES.NOMNOUTPUTS: Akukho ziphumo zeMasternode ezifunyenweyo. Ukuqhuba i-Masternode yengingqi uthumele ngqo i-2,5,25,50 okanye i-100 yezigidi zeengqekembe kwidilesi yakho ye-Masternode kwaye ulinde isiqinisekiso se-15.

SIGNMESSAGE.SIGN_DESCRIPTION: Ungayayina imilayezo kunye needesi zakho ukuze uzibonakalise ungumnikazi wazo. Qaphela ukuba ungasayineli into engacacileyo, njengoko ukuhlaselwa kwe-phishing kungazama ukukhohlisa ukuba ungayinayina ubunikazi kubo. Bhalisa kuphela izitatimende ezipheleleyo iinkcukacha ozivumayo.
SIGNMESSAGE.VERIFY_DESCRIPTION: Faka idilesi yokutyikitya, umyalezo (qinisekisa ukukopisha ikhefu, izikhala, iithebhu, njl njl njl njl njl) kunye nesayine engezantsi ukuqinisekisa umyalezo. Qaphela ukuba ungayifunde ngakumbi kwisayinitsha kunokuba yintoni umyalezo osayinwe ngokwawo, ukuphepha ukukhohliswa ngumntu ophakathi kokuhlaselwa.

DEBUG.CONSOLEINFO: Wamkelekile kwikhonsoli ye-Metrix Core RPC. Thayipha uncedo malunga nokujonga ngokubanzi imiyalelo ekhoyo.
DEBUG.CONSOLEWARNING: ISEXWAYISO: Abadlali be-scammers baye basebenzayo, bathetha abasebenzisi ukuba bafake imiyalelo apha, beba okuqukethwe kwekhredithi. Ungayisebenzisi le console ngaphandle kokuqonda ngokupheleleyo ukuhluthwa komyalelo.

REPAIR.INFOEXTERNAL: Le miyalelo yokulungisa ayikwazi ukusebenza xa uMetrix Core iqhutywe ngaphandle
REPAIR.INFO: Amaqhosha angezantsi aya kuqala kwakhona iMetrix Core ngeendlela zokwenza umyalelo wokulungisa i-wallet, imiba yokulungisa kunye neefayili ze-blockchain ezikhohlakeleyo okanye izinto ezingekho phantsi / ezingekho phantsi.
REPAIR.RECOVER1INFO: -zapwallettxes = 1: Ukubuyisela ukuthengiselana kwi-blockchain (gcina i-meta-data, umz. umnikazi we-akhawunti)
REPAIR.UPGRADEWALLETINFO: -upgradewallet: Ukulungiswa kwesikhwama sefomathi ukuya kufomathi yamuva ekuqaleni. (Qaphela: oku akusikho ukuhlaziywa kwekhredithi ngokwayo!)
REPAIR.REBUILDINDEXINFO: -reindex: Yakha kwakhona i-blockchain index ukusuka kwii-fk000 zamanje.
REPAIR.BOOTSTRAPINFO: Ukukhuphela iifayile ze-Metrix blockchain ukusuka kwi-metrixcoin.com kunye ne-bootstrap kufakelo lwakho. Kuxhomekeke kunxibelelwano lwakho lwenethiwekhi oku kunokuthatha imizuzu eli-10 ukuya kwiiyure ezimbalwa
REPAIR.SYNCFROMSTARTINFO: Cima iifayile zakho zebhlokhi yendawo yakho kwaye uphinde ungene kwi-genesis block.
REPAIR.RESTARTCOREINFO: Qalisa kwakhona i-Metrix Core ukuba sele isebenza okanye iqalisa iMetrix Core ukuba ayisebenzi.
REPAIR.REINSTALLCOREINFO: Cima i-Metrix Core yendawo yakho kwaye uyifake kwakhona kwiiseva zeMetrix.

PROMPT.CLIENTUPDATEINFO: Uhlaziyo lufumaneka kwiMetrix Core. Ungathanda ukuyifaka ngoku?
PROMPT.WALLETUPDATEINFO: Uhlaziyo lufumaneka kwi-Altitude. Ungathanda ukuyikhuphela ngoku?
PROMPT.CLIENTSTOPPEDINFO: Uxhumano luye lwalahleka kwiMetrix Core. Unokumisa isikhwama okanye uqale uMetrix Core yangaphakathi.
PROMPT.ENCRYPTEDCONTENT: Naliphi na i-backups ezenziwe ngaphambili kwifayili yakho yekhredithi kufuneka ithathelwe indawo kunye nefayili yesikhwama esikhankanywe ngokutsha. Ngenxa yezizathu zokhuseleko, iifayile zangaphambili zefayili yefayile engenakunceda ziza kuba zingenakuncedo ngokukhawuleza xa uqala ukusebenzisa i-wallet entsha.
PROMPT.CLIENTCLOSEDUNEXPECTEDINFO: Kwakukho ingxaki neMetrix Core eyenze ukuba ipheliswe. Kucetyiswa ukuba ujonge ifayile yakho debug.log ngemicimbi.
PROMPT.CLIENTINVALIDCONFIGINFO: I-metrix.conf yakho ine-setup yamasternode engavumelekanga eya kwenza uMetrix Core ukuba aphume ngokukhawuleza. Nceda khangela le fayile.
PROMPT.BOOTSTRAPFAILEDINFO: Kwakukho ingxaki yokuqalisa i-Metrix Core. Kucetyiswa ukuba ujonge ifayile yelog yeAltitude kwimicimbi.
PROMPT.STARTUPFAILEDINFO: Kwakukho ukuqala kweMetrix Core. Kucetyiswa ukuba ujonge ifayile yelog yeAltitude kwimicimbi.
PROMPT.CLIENTUNKNOWNERRORINFO: Kwakukho ingxaki yokunxibelelana neMetrix Core. Kucetyiswa ukuba ujonge ifayile yakho debug.log ngemicimbi.
PROMPT.UNENROLLGOVERNORCONTENT: Uqinisekile ufuna ukubhalisa iRhuluneli yakho? Awusayi kuphinda uvote kulawulo lwetyathanga.

ADDRESSBOOK.SENDINGINFO: Le yile dilesi yakho yeLinda egcinwe ukuthumela iintlawulo. Njalo ukhangele imali kunye nokwamkela idilesi ngaphambi kokuthumela iimali
ADDRESSBOOK.RECEIVINGINFO: Le yile dilesi yeLinda yakho yokufumana iintlawulo.

MAINCHAINCHECK.ALERT: Isilumkiso! Awukho kwikhonkco eliphambili ngokuhambelana nomhloli weMetrix. Kunconywe kakhulu ukuphinda kuvumelaniswe okanye kusebenze kwakhona kwi-blockchain yakho ukuthintela ukulahleka kwazo nayiphi na ingqekembe.

NOTIFICATIONS.CHECKINGUPDATEFAILED: Ayikwazi ukuhlola ukuhlaziywa. Hlola intanethi yakho.

NOTIFICATIONS.INSUFFICIENTBALANCE: Ibhalansi enganeleyo ekhethiweyo ukugqiba lo msebenzi
NOTIFICATIONS.GENERICERROR: Iphutha elingaziwa lenzeke. Ungadinga ukuqala kwakhona i-wallet yakho kwaye uzame kwakhona. Ukuba iingxaki ziyaqhubeka ziqhagamshelane nenkxaso.
NOTIFICATIONS.MINIMUMCONFIRMATIONS: Zonke iziphumo zifuna okungenani 1 ukuqinisekiswa ngaphambi kokuchitha.
NOTIFICATIONS.FAILEDTOWRITECONFIG: Kwakukho ingxaki yokubhala kwifayile yakho ye-metrix.conf. Jonga ifayile ekhoyo kunye nokuba Altitude ineemvume zokubhala.
NOTIFICATIONS.NOPUBLICUP: Akukho dilesi ye-IP kawonkewonke efunyenweyo. Jonga uqhagamshelo lwakho lweintanethi kwaye uqalise kwakhona Altitude.
NOTIFICATIONS.REPORTINGISSUE: Ukufumana ulwazi lokuqonda... Olu lwazi luya kukotshwa kwibhodi yakho.

GOVERNANCE.NOTGOVERNORDETAIL: Iirhuluneli zinoxanduva lokuvota kuhlahlo-lwabiwo mali lwenyanga kunye notshintsho lwebloko. Unokuba yi-Rhuluneli ngokutshixa isivumelwano esifanelekileyo kwikhontrakthi yoLawulo.
GOVERNANCE.CONFIRMENROLL: Ngoku sowuza kubhalisa njengoRhuluneli. Oku kuyakuthumela ukuthengiselana ngesivumelwano esifanelekileyo kwisivumelwano solawulo. Awunakho ukubhalisa nangaliphi na ixesha.
GOVERNANCE.ISGOVERNORDETAIL1: Iirhuluneli zinoxanduva lokuvota kuhlahlo-lwabiwo mali lwenyanga kunye notshintsho lwebloko.
GOVERNANCE.ISGOVERNORDETAIL2: Ukuhlala iRhuluneli kuyakufuneka uthathe inxaxheba okungenani kwiivoti ezingama-30.
GOVERNANCE.ISGOVERNORDETAIL3: Ukuba akukho nto uvotayo kuyo, ungakuqhubeka ngesandla ukubhalisa ngokuthumela i-ping esebenzayo.
